import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.countplot(x="Gram_Staining", data=data, palette="Set2")
    ax.set(xlabel='Gram Staining', ylabel='Count of Bacteria')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of bacteria based on their Gram Staining?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x="Penicillin", y="Streptomycin", data=data)
    ax.axhline(data['Streptomycin'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Streptomycin Mean')
    ax.axvline(data['Penicillin'].mean(), color='green', linestyle='--', label='Penicillin Mean')
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    chart = sns.boxplot(x="Genus", y="Neomycin", data=data)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, horizontalalignment='right')
    plt.title("What is the distribution of Neomycin effectiveness across different genera of bacteria?", wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(y=data['Neomycin'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median Neomycin Effectiveness: {:.2f}'.format(data['Neomycin'].median()))
    plt.legend(loc='best')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    data = data[['Penicillin', 'Streptomycin', 'Neomycin', 'Bacteria']]
    data = data.groupby(['Bacteria']).sum().reset_index()
    data = pd.melt(data, id_vars=['Bacteria'], value_vars=['Penicillin', 'Streptomycin', 'Neomycin'], var_name='Antibiotic', value_name='Count')
    ax = sns.barplot(x='Bacteria', y='Count', hue='Antibiotic', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the overall effectiveness of Penicillin, Streptomycin and Neomycin against all bacteria?', wrap=True)
    ax.set(xlabel='Bacteria', ylabel='Count')
    ax.legend(title='Antibiotic')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
